<!doctype html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>인트봇 공식 상점</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no">
    
    <link href="/shop.css" rel="stylesheet">
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="pricing-header px-3 py-3 pt-md-5 pb-md-4 mx-auto text-center">
      <h1 class="display-4">상점</h1><br>
      <p class="lead">인트봇에서 얻은 돈으로 상품을 사세요.</p>
      <p class="lead"><b><%= user.name %></b> 님의 돈: <b><%= user.money %> 원</b></p>
    </div>

    <div class="container">
      <div class="card-deck mb-3 text-center">
        <div class="card mb-4 box-shadow">
          <div class="card-header">
            <h4 class="my-0 font-weight-normal">테스트</h4>
          </div>
          <div class="card-body">
            <h1 class="card-title pricing-card-title">1000원</h1>
            <ul class="list-unstyled mt-3 mb-4">
              <li>&nbsp;</li>
              <li>테스트 상품입니다.</li>
              <li>&nbsp;</li>
            </ul>
            <button class="btn btn-primary " onclick="location.href='/buy_process?code=<%= code %>&itemID=test1'">구입</button>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>

